summary: This is a calendar entry for a telephone conference regarding jury selection in the Ghislaine Maxwell case, scheduled for October 21, 2021. It shows planning for the trial logistics and lists an organizer and an attendee by internal identifier.

events.title: Maxwell Jury Selection Telephone Conference
events.description: A scheduled telephone conference to discuss jury selection for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.

keyFacts: A jury selection planning call for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial was scheduled for October 21, 2021.
The document is a calendar entry created on August 27, 2021, and later modified on the day of the event.
The entry lists an 'Organizer' and an 'Attendee' referenced by internal identifiers (EFTA00155145), not by personal names.
